    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Polymeric fiber having a width of less than 1000 nanometers. The material may be fashioned into nanotextiles which have advantageous properties such as extreme water-resistance and elasticity. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
